Strongly recommend Dr. Dolly to anyone looking for Quality, Painless and long term solution for your teeth! She is technically sound, detail oriented and explains the issue really well. No unnecessary procedure if not required. She is one of the best in the industry and what adds to the positive experience is her friendly and calm demeanor and patience while you explain your problem.
Thanks for the great experience. Never thought visiting a dentist can be so pleasant:) Best wishes to her !!

A great and painless experience at the clinic. Dr. Dolly was very patient and took care to explain the procedure and the complexities. 

The clinic is so beautiful and green. The aura is very positive and clean. 

I am very happy with my treatment and results. Would recommend to everyone.

I visited Dr.Dolly Gupta last week,and i must say she's filled with knowledge and experience, i was facing Problem in my teeth and was suffering with unbearable pain and that's how she recommended RCT for my tooth, and after three visits now I am completely fine and free with pain. I really recommend  Dr.Dolly Gupta for futher dental problems.

The doctor’s approachable nature was so helpful as she went out of her way to advise me even at an odd hour which really helped me in my misery. Most accurate diagnosis and advise is difficult to find now a days but Dr Dolly Gupta is the undiscovered gem who is most reliable.

Best part about Dr. Dolly is that she is very friendly and explains the treatment very well. Got the scalling and dental fillings done from her. It was a commendable job done by her. I already recommended her to one of my friend and will continue to do so.
